metadata.name: KING ROMULUS
metadata.description:
Sango seeks to Celebrate and give Recognition to king Romulus for his support, encouragement and for being an inspiration for new and incoming artist and collectors alike in the NFT community. A king and war general, a force to be reckoned with, leading artists and creators to war and making sure they record victory in their respective projects and in turn inviting others to join.  
With this piece I represent king as one of the powerful warriors of OYO empire - SANGO. A king and a warlord who has lead his kingdom to victories and conquered a lot of kingdoms.  
This striking personalities is what lead to the inspiration behind this piece and a gift for a friend, a supporter and source of inspiration for the community.
